1.0.name: wordpress/tgfinet-seo
1.0.description:
Override titles, descriptions and keywords with page/post level input for greater control of Search Engine Optimization.

This is a fairly modified version of the all-in-one-seo-pack for the specific situation of using Wordpress as a CMS tool first and a blog second. We fixed some quirky duplication of title and meta info as well.

Download the latest now!

Some features:

  • Override titles, descriptions and keywords with page/post level input for greater control of Search Engine Optimization.
  • Auto-generate titles, descriptions and keywords when overrides are not present.
  • Helps prevent duplicate content issues.
  • Automatically appends tags as keywords when available.
  • Makes sure your keywords are unique.
  • Page and post level
